             were indicted for <rs id="t18090215-9-off36" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18090215-9-off36" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18090215-9-off36" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t18090215-9-cd37" type="crimeDate">4th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18090215-9-off36 t18090215-9-cd37"></join>, eight yards of muslin, value 11 s. 4 d. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18090215-9-victim117" type="victimName">
                           Francis 
                           Cole
                        <interp inst="t18090215-9-victim117" type="surname" value="Cole"></interp>
